## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of human trafficking prevention. The information is subject to change as new strategies and technologies emerge. Additionally, the effectiveness of prevention strategies can vary based on regional and cultural contexts, which are not fully explored in this report.